{
  "stem": "16503.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm not saying that I was visualizing myself somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean disconnect, and I think that's what people must-- the ones who looked so disciplined in that particular train must have done because we didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't have no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were squeezed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was mostly completely dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We arrived somewhere, finally, and we heard enormous amount of screaming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we heard the doors being opened, the sealed doors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The SS was just crawling around, just absolutely crawling with bayonets and the butts of the-- of their rifles.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I hope I will never ever see a picture like that because when we came finally to the door to disembark, if you can call it that, or be thrown own out from the cattle car, first of all, you didn't see properly because now you had a daylight.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was very cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was-- though the car was very stinky, this was even stinkier where we were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all we saw was-- well, all I saw was this barbed wire with figures, not even people, standing behind the barbed wires-- skeletons with a striped uniform hanging with a cap on the head, and a face, which was not a face, and eyes, which were empty.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And do you know that to this day, I have got a very hard time to look into people's eyes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you ask me what color of eyes somebody has, I will not know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the reason is I came to the conclusion-- after 50 years, believe it or not-- was the shock of this absolute emptiness and nothingness of these poor creatures which were standing behind the barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
